  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Informed consent,

          -  Signs or symptoms of indication of acute bacterial diarrhea (traveller's diarrhea)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Fever,

          -  Grossly bloody stool,

          -  Females pregnant or breast feeding,

          -  Participation in an other clinical trial
      </textblock>
